OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.NAME: Frequency
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.DESCRIPTION: The number of times something occurs during a specified time period.
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.HELP: The frequency is used in conjunction with the frequency type in determining an event. Example: If the Frequency Type is Week and the Frequency is 2 - it is every two weeks.
